## Testing Components

Create a test file: `test/features/<feature>/presentation/widgets/<component>_test.dart`

```dart
import 'package:flutter/material.dart';
import 'package:flutter_test/flutter_test.dart';
import 'package:user_app/features/.../component.widget.dart';

void main() {
  testWidgets('ComponentName displays title', (tester) async {
    await tester.pumpWidget(
      MaterialApp(
        home: Scaffold(
          body: ComponentName(title: 'Test Title'),
        ),
      ),
    );

    expect(find.text('Test Title'), findsOneWidget);
  });
}
```

After creating component:
1. Show the user the file location
2. Explain the properties and usage
3. Provide example usage code
4. Suggest where to import it from
5. Offer to create a test file
